	}
	.@id = getarg(0);							//Item ID

	setd ".eStat_"+.@id,.@count;				//Slot Count
	setd ".eStat_"+.@id+"_OW",getarg(1);		//Overwrite?
	setd ".eStat_"+.@id+"_CostID",getarg(2);	//Cost ID
	setd ".eStat_"+.@id+"_CostAmt",getarg(3);	//Cost Amount

	}

	return;
}
